    • QR

      protected static Matrix[] QR​(Matrix A, boolean countHouseholder)
      Factors a matrix A into an orthogonal matrix Q and an upper triangular matrix R such that A=QR.
      Parameters:
      A - - Matrix to factor into QR.
      Returns:
      QR factorization of the matrix A as an array of matrices of length 2. The first element of the array will be Q and the second will be R.
